text: The Topolog Viaduct is a viaduct east of Râmnicu Vâlcea over the river Topolog. The bridge was opened in 1989. The viaduct is 1,440 m in length; it has a main height of around 50 m, being constructed out of reinforced concrete. == External links == * Description Category:Bridges completed in 1989 Category:Buildings and structures in Vâlcea County Category:Concrete bridges Category:Railway bridges in Romania Category:Viaducts in Romania
